+- Execution ID
+- Order ID
+- Market condition reference
+- Average fill price
+- Best available market price
+- Bid/ask spread
+- Fill percentage
+- Commission
+- Slippage and market impact
+- Order type
+- Asset class
+- Session label
+
+Execution Quality remains evaluative only. It does not create fills, mutate orders, or compute portfolio performance.
