+# OR-006 Recovery Architecture
+
+Recovery is handled by `DurableEnterprisePersistenceStore.recover_runtime()`.
+
+Recovery steps:
+
+1. Validate repository hash chains and entity identity.
+2. Construct a fresh `CanonicalEnterpriseRuntime`.
